code: @Override protected SubtaskExecutionAttemptDetailsInfo handleRequest(HandlerRequest<EmptyRequestBody, SubtaskMessageParameters> request, AccessExecutionVertex executionVertex) throws RestHandlerException {     final AccessExecution execution = executionVertex.getCurrentExecutionAttempt().     final MutableIOMetrics ioMetrics = new MutableIOMetrics().     final JobID jobID = request.getPathParameter(JobIDPathParameter.class).     final JobVertexID jobVertexID = request.getPathParameter(JobVertexIdPathParameter.class).     ioMetrics.addIOMetrics(execution, metricFetcher, jobID.toString(), jobVertexID.toString()).     return SubtaskExecutionAttemptDetailsInfo.create(execution, ioMetrics). }
